sonar_blocker_violations.title: Blocker Violations

comment_lines.title: Comment Lines

loc.title: Number of Lines

sonar_lines_to_cover.description: Number of lines of code which could be covered by unit tests

line_coverage.title: Line Coverage
line_coverage.description: Density of fully covered lines of code
